<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/07-12-96/sf0797.html 199.173.162.110 19970215020811 text/html 21381
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 02:04:07 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 05-Dec-96 19:08:49 GMT
Content-length: 21193
