<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/16-11-96/wb8443.html 199.173.162.110 19970215022213 text/html 11328
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 02:18:07 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Nov-96 19:00:13 GMT
