<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/09-11-96/am3111.html 199.173.162.110 19970215022612 text/html 7430
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 02:22:07 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Nov-96 17:45:17 GMT
Content-length: 7243
