<DOCOLDNO>IA096-001031-B030-289</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/02-11-96/br7563.html 199.173.162.110 19970215023141 text/html 4184
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 02:27:37 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 31-Oct-96 17:31:39 GMT
Content-length: 3997
