http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/26-10-96/bw0757.html 199.173.162.110 19970215023332 text/html 6720
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 02:29:26 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 25-Oct-96 10:33:28 GMT
