<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/19-10-96/st4060.html 199.173.162.110 19970215023949 text/html 9267
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 02:35:46 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 17-Oct-96 16:04:11 GMT
