<html><head><title>Election Billboard</title></head><body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<center><p align=center>
<img src="http://www.economist.com/econlogosmall.gif" width="78" height="39" alt="The Economist" border=0></p><p align=center>
<img src="../images/am.gif" width="258" height="26" alt="American Survey" border=0>
