<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/05-10-96/st4052.html 199.173.162.110 19970215024812 text/html 8759
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 02:44:10 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 03-Oct-96 19:49:31 GMT
