<DOCHDR>
http://www.europe.economist.com:80/issue/31-08-96/ld1.html 199.173.162.110 19970215030624 text/html 8135
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 03:02:19 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 29-Aug-96 18:02:00 GMT
